description:
Kochou Kanae was a Demon Slayer and the late Flower Pillar, slain several years prior to the present story. She was also the biological older sister of http://anidb.net/ch105764 [Kochou Shinobu] and the adoptive older sister of http://anidb.net/ch105763 [Tsuyuri Kanao].
Source: Kimetsu no Yaiba Wiki
name: Kochou Kanae
